{"type": "article", "id": 34447, "title": "换个灯泡，台灯就成了充电器｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-14T23:07:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 24382, "name": "Simon Legald"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 86, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161114221251ZGJYrHnBD2sTEeyl.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Senik by Sailee Adhao</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>身陷火场，谁还有时间去阅读灭火器上的使用说明书呢？印度设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/saileeadhao\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sailee Adhao</a> 带来的概念灭火器 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/44579553/Senik-Fire-Extinguisher-Redesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Senik</a> 就是基于人们慌乱中的本能反应打造的，而且单手就能提起。如果发生火情，只要用力敲打黄色的三角形隔断，将其内部的亚克力小块击碎后就能把灭火器从架子上取出了。在上下两部分连接起来之后，灭火器内部的构造就会联通，从而产生化学反应喷射出水雾。中间弯折的造型能让内部的水持续向下流，提高了利用率。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171036h7tWgR3DxBJPQZi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171036seytmc8drK4kpvw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.152381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171036aPkxLFbWMf3rc7RO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171036b3KFlQuHpvs1WrBS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171036e5910IvDuRzF7Gpq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.055238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171037JPuwKexCtaX93RDE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.638095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Trash Interceptor by Huang Yi-Chang</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>城市的下水道系统难免会堆积不少垃圾，工人们每天都要耗费大量的时间精力去打开盖子进行清理。为了让环卫工人们能够轻松地完成工作，来自台湾华梵大学的 Huang Yi-Chang 设计了 <a href=\"http://ifworlddesignguide.com/entry/195060-trash-interceptor\" rel=\"nofollow\">Trash Interceptor</a> 垃圾过滤器。它是一个放在井盖下的箱子， 逆水流方向摆放后垃圾就留在滤网下的黄色篮子中。如此一来，环卫工人只需要打开井盖拉起把手将垃圾清理掉即可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611141706439rjxpdtl4QkJsqA6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170643FhAjz6py28RLoDud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.244762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170643b8rnie2fga7RP4T1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170643tduLh0fCjb3v4nTl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.963810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PowerBulb by Mega Tiny Corp.</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>为了连上插座，你或许也经历过在办公室或是旅馆内不得不移动家具或是带上接线板的经历。美国公司 <a href=\"http://megatinycorp.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mega Tiny</a> 最近对灯泡进行了一番改造，创造出一种全新的充电方式。这个名叫 PowerBulb 的灯泡有一个特殊的底座，它自带两个 USB 端口，可以提供照明的同时为你的设备充电。这个仅重 320 克的灯泡能在所有 E26 和 E27 灯头上使用，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/megatiny/powerbulb-led-light-bulb-with-two-usb-charging-por\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 29 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170621toSbi9xIdXkHMjL6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.572901\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170622YlLBgQpiAwk7D6rx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111417062268QGSBP1WzdFYp3u.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.544118\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611141706215GEMeLkxlsD2c7pW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.047198\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170621whCH5B3DPs6kOJ1t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668142\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Terra tables by Simon Legald</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>提到水磨石，你想到的或许是地面，最近丹麦设计师 <a href=\"http://www.simonlegald.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Simon Legald</a> 用这种材料为 <a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Normann Copenhagen</a> 设计了一套带有精美石斑的桌子 Terra。由于每块石头的图案都不一样，成品也都是独一无二的。除了水磨石台面外，Terra 的螺旋型桌腿也借助了“非常规”的加工技术，它往往会使用在制作栏杆和门上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170608IkYWSoPVaZ2Kspwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562183\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170608sjkTH2PzDREx1tKG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170608PejtMJxIkNamfLEb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170608lDzpEo54sB70HedF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Chaos by Alessandro Criscito</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>这款名为 Chaos 的柜子是智利设计师 <a href=\"http://www.tevasq.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessandro Criscito</a> 的作品，用包围着木制框架的宽大橡皮筋来替代柜门是它的一大特色。杂乱无章的黑色橡皮筋刚好和黑色的金属底座形成对比，透过缝隙可以隐约看到内部的设计为它增添了一股神秘感，同时也鼓励用户与家具进行互动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171224I1bjfVsatrn0uJzL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171224w2WFepL6Yn4suqcb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171224gyuQrXDOtEG4LmVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114171224arLqbT72iP1XzS4l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lavazza Coffee by Issac Fusté</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>西班牙设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/IsaacFuste\" rel=\"nofollow\">Issac Fusté</a> 为意大利咖啡品牌 <a href=\"http://www.lavazza.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lavazza</a> 设计了一组风格简洁的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/13091111/Packaging-Gourmet-Lavazza\" rel=\"nofollow\">包装</a>，通过泡咖啡工具和装满咖啡的杯子的俯视照，以另一种角度观察日常生活中的咖啡文化。而在高端产品线的包装设计上，Fusté 则改用了黑白色以体现出更高级的感觉，雕塑照片则代表了品牌的意大利血统。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170550zo6EaFwCik3ON4uj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170550Z6oQTf2zU3tg84xY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170550Z5JRwGIA4Xs9BjLy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161114170551LTwMyn1hX6xWiajo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}